    "Looks up an approximate location from your IP address. Coarse — typically city-level." : {
      "comment" : "Weather location source explanation.",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Looks up an approximate location from your IP address. Coarse — typically city-level."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "IP アドレスからおおよその位置を調べます。粗い精度 — 通常は市区町村レベルです。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "根据 IP 地址查找大致位置。精度较粗，通常到城市级。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "從你的 IP 位址查詢大略位置。精度較粗 — 通常到城市層級。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "macOS always picks hardware vs. software decode itself — apps cannot force a choice. This control instead caps the resolution and bitrate AVPlayer is allowed to request, which is what actually moves the GPU / battery dial." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "macOS always picks hardware vs. software decode itself — apps cannot force a choice. This control instead caps the resolution and bitrate AVPlayer is allowed to request, which is what actually moves the GPU / battery dial."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "macOS はハードウェア／ソフトウェアデコーダーを常に自動選択するため、アプリ側では強制できません。この設定では代わりに AVPlayer が要求できる解像度とビットレートに上限をかけ、GPU 負荷とバッテリー消費を実際にコントロールします。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "macOS 始终自己决定使用硬件还是软件解码——app 无法强制。这个选项实际是限制 AVPlayer 能请求的分辨率和码率，从而真正影响 GPU 负载和电池消耗。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "macOS 始終自行決定使用硬體還是軟體解碼——app 無法強制。這個選項實際是限制 AVPlayer 能請求的解析度與位元率，從而真正影響 GPU 負載與電池消耗。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "macOS can't load Windows native plugins." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "macOS can't load Windows native plugins."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "macOS では Windows ネイティブプラグインを読み込めません。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "macOS 无法加载 Windows 原生插件。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "macOS 無法載入 Windows 原生外掛。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "macOS couldn't grant the app secure access to that file. Try a different video, or move the file to a folder you own." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "macOS couldn't grant the app secure access to that file. Try a different video, or move the file to a folder you own."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "macOS がこのファイルへのセキュアアクセスを許可できませんでした。別のビデオを試すか、ご自身のフォルダにファイルを移動してください。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "macOS 无法授予此应用访问该文件的安全权限。换一个视频，或将文件移到你自己的文件夹下再试。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "macOS 無法授予此 App 存取該檔案的安全權限。換一個影片，或將檔案移到您自己的資料夾下再試。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "macOS couldn't grant the app secure access to that resource. Try moving it to a folder you own." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "macOS couldn't grant the app secure access to that resource. Try moving it to a folder you own."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "macOS がこのリソースへのセキュアアクセスを許可できませんでした。ご自身のフォルダに移動してから再試行してください。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "macOS 无法授予此应用访问该资源的安全权限。请将其移到你自己的文件夹下再试。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "macOS 無法授予此 App 存取該資源的安全權限。請將其移到您自己的資料夾下再試。"
          }
        }
