            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "LiveWallpaper の改善にご協力いただきありがとうございます。下記の情報は GitHub issue に事前入力されます。**投稿前に内容をご確認ください** — issue は誰でも閲覧できます。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "感谢帮助 LiveWallpaper 改进。下方信息会预填到 GitHub issue 里。**提交前请检查一遍** — issue 一旦创建任何人都能看到。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "感謝協助 LiveWallpaper 改進。下方資訊會預先填入 GitHub issue。**送出前請先檢查** — issue 一旦建立任何人都能看到。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "That preset overlaps an existing slot. Adjust an existing slot first." : {
      "comment" : "Schedule error shown when a preset can't be applied because it overlaps.",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
