          }
        }
      }
    },
    "These shortcuts work even when LiveWallpaper is in the background. Bare keys without a modifier are rejected (they would steal regular typing), and two actions can't share the same combination. Conflicts with system or other-app shortcuts will silently take whichever app registers first — pick a different combination if a shortcut doesn't trigger." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "These shortcuts work even when LiveWallpaper is in the background. Bare keys without a modifier are rejected (they would steal regular typing), and two actions can't share the same combination. Conflicts with system or other-app shortcuts will silently take whichever app registers first — pick a different combination if a shortcut doesn't trigger."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "これらのショートカットは、LiveWallpaper がバックグラウンドにあるときも動作します。修飾キーのない単独キーは通常の入力を奪うため拒否され、2 つのアクションで同じ組み合わせは使えません。システムや他のアプリのショートカットと競合した場合は、先に登録したアプリが暗黙的に優先されます。ショートカットが反応しない場合は、別の組み合わせを選んでください。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "即使 LiveWallpaper 在后台运行，这些快捷键也能工作。不带修饰键的裸键会被拒绝（它们会干扰正常输入），且两个操作不能共用同一组合。与系统或其他应用的快捷键冲突时，会静默采用先注册的应用——如果快捷键没有触发，请选择其他组合。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "即使 LiveWallpaper 在背景執行，這些快捷鍵也能運作。不含輔助鍵的單鍵會被拒絕（它們會攔截一般輸入），且兩個動作不能共用相同組合。若與系統或其他 App 的快捷鍵衝突，會靜默採用先註冊的 App；如果快捷鍵未觸發，請改選其他組合。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This allows the wallpaper to run scripts, use local storage, and access WebGPU. Only trust origins you recognize." : {
      "comment" : "Body text of the Trust confirmation dialog.",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This allows the wallpaper to run scripts, use local storage, and access WebGPU. Only trust origins you recognize."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "壁紙がスクリプトの実行、ローカルストレージの使用、WebGPU へのアクセスを行えるようになります。信頼できるオリジンのみを許可してください。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "这将允许壁纸运行脚本、使用本地存储和访问 WebGPU。仅信任你信赖的来源。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "這將允許桌布執行腳本、使用本機儲存空間並存取 WebGPU。只信任你信賴的來源。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This configuration is for a different app (%@). Expected %@." : {
      "comment" : "Import failure: bundle identifier doesn't match.",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This configuration is for a different app (%1$@). Expected %2$@."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "この構成は別のアプリ（%1$@）用です。想定：%2$@。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此配置适用于其他应用（%1$@）。预期为 %2$@。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此設定適用於其他 App（%1$@）。預期為 %2$@。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This configuration was made with a different version (schema %lld). This build supports schema 1 through %lld." : {
      "comment" : "Import failure: schema is outside the supported range.",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This configuration was made with a different version (schema %1$lld). This build supports schema 1 through %2$lld."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "この構成は別のバージョン（スキーマ %1$lld）で作成されています。このビルドはスキーマ 1 から %2$lld まで対応しています。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此配置由其他版本创建（架构 %1$lld）。此版本支持架构 1 到 %2$lld。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此設定是以不同版本建立的（結構描述 %1$lld）。此版本支援結構描述 1 到 %2$lld。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This file is too large to import (%lld bytes). Configuration backups are usually well under 10 MB." : {
      "comment" : "Import failure: the file exceeds the size cap and is likely not a real config bundle.",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This file is too large to import (%lld bytes). Configuration backups are usually well under 10 MB."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "このファイルは大きすぎてインポートできません（%lld バイト）。構成バックアップは通常 10 MB を大きく下回ります。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此文件太大，无法导入（%lld 字节）。配置备份通常远小于 10 MB。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此檔案太大，無法匯入（%lld 位元組）。設定備份通常遠小於 10 MB。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This format requires Metal-backed GPU decoding that this Mac doesn't support. Try rendering on a newer GPU." : {
      "comment" : "Wallpaper Engine fallback warning body.",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This format requires Metal-backed GPU decoding that this Mac doesn't support. Try rendering on a newer GPU."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "この形式には Metal ベースの GPU デコードが必要ですが、この Mac では対応していません。より新しい GPU でレンダリングしてみてください。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此格式需要此 Mac 不支持的 Metal GPU 解码。请尝试在较新的 GPU 上渲染。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此格式需要 Metal 支援的 GPU 解碼，但這台 Mac 不支援。請嘗試在較新的 GPU 上渲染。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This scene uses a custom shader the renderer couldn't translate to Metal. Try re-downloading the project in Steam." : {
      "comment" : "Wallpaper Engine fallback warning body.",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This scene uses a custom shader the renderer couldn't translate to Metal. Try re-downloading the project in Steam."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "このシーンは、レンダラーが Metal に変換できないカスタムシェーダーを使用しています。Steam でプロジェクトを再ダウンロードしてみてください。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此场景使用了渲染器无法转译为 Metal 的自定义着色器。请尝试在 Steam 中重新下载该项目。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此場景使用了渲染器無法轉譯為 Metal 的自訂著色器。請嘗試在 Steam 中重新下載此專案。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This wallpaper bundles a Windows `.dll` plugin (e.g. an audio visualizer or screensaver runtime). macOS can't load Windows native code, so the project is permanently unsupported here." : {
      "comment" : "Wallpaper Engine fallback warning body.",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This wallpaper bundles a Windows `.dll` plugin (e.g. an audio visualizer or screensaver runtime). macOS can't load Windows native code, so the project is permanently unsupported here."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "この壁紙には Windows の `.dll` プラグイン（オーディオビジュアライザーやスクリーンセーバーランタイムなど）が含まれています。macOS は Windows ネイティブコードを読み込めないため、このプロジェクトはここでは永続的に非対応です。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此壁纸捆绑了 Windows `.dll` 插件（例如音频可视化器或屏保运行时）。macOS 无法加载 Windows 原生代码，因此此项目在这里无法支持。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此桌布包含 Windows `.dll` 外掛程式（例如音訊視覺化工具或螢幕保護程式執行階段）。macOS 無法載入 Windows 原生程式碼，因此此專案在此永久不受支援。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This Wallpaper Engine project type isn't supported yet. Try a Video or Web variant." : {
      "comment" : "Inline error shown in onboarding when a WPE project type is unsupported.",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This Wallpaper Engine project type isn't supported yet. Try a Video or Web variant."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "この Wallpaper Engine プロジェクトタイプにはまだ対応していません。動画または Web 版を試してください。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "尚不支持此 Wallpaper Engine 项目类型。请尝试视频或网页版本。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "尚不支援此 Wallpaper Engine 專案類型。請嘗試影片或 Web 版本。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This wallpaper needs Wallpaper Engine's own 3D rendering engine to play. We're working on broader Phase 2 support — your other wallpapers continue to play unaffected." : {
      "comment" : "Wallpaper Engine fallback warning body.",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This wallpaper needs Wallpaper Engine's own 3D rendering engine to play. We're working on broader Phase 2 support — your other wallpapers continue to play unaffected."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "この壁紙の再生には Wallpaper Engine 独自の 3D レンダリングエンジンが必要です。Phase 2 の対応範囲を拡大中です。他の壁紙は影響を受けずに再生されます。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此壁纸需要 Wallpaper Engine 自带的 3D 渲染引擎才能播放。我们正在扩展 Phase 2 支持，其他壁纸会继续正常播放。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此桌布需要 Wallpaper Engine 自己的 3D 渲染引擎才能播放。我們正在擴充 Phase 2 支援；你的其他桌布會照常播放，不受影響。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This wallpaper relies on other Workshop projects we don't have on disk yet. Subscribe to them in Steam, then re-import this folder." : {
      "comment" : "Wallpaper Engine fallback warning body.",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
